1:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩係日本返黎, 食左幾餐老麥<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地全撚部人都會自己執盤</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n仲要自己做垃圾分類"},{"pid":"07b7c0e91ff1cf3f7db06fd98eccd1efe6c44e1a","tid":399911,"uid":4360,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"普通舖唔執，大學範圍內就執<br />\n享用咗折扣就有義務執<br />\n其他？我俾嗰個價錢包咗請人執tray架"},{"pid":"2b3285db2f538409ae0dcd681cf9f66767154193","tid":399911,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:12:14.000Z","msg":"M記呀姐會屌鳩你"},{"pid":"2a640ae00d80cd01554bbccafe084edd9811c2d9","tid":399911,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:15:00.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間會<br />\n無乜人就唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb81ac88a8f972e835145b3d08eeeea598417abc","tid":399911,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:17:35.000Z","msg":"屌你 自己執返手尾好基本啦"},{"pid":"1beb3e8907669874e55a45282e624a8a127760f3","tid":399911,"uid":130032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實如果唔洗掂到垃圾筒，執一執都無乜所謂。<br />\n唔明點解唔用類似食環放係街開口個款垃圾筒。</blockquote><br />\n食環指引一定要有蓋垃圾桶"},{"pid":"8aecf090b73d2b76d32bef804cd6061912299abc","tid":399911,"uid":144157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:22:18.000Z","msg":"係日本食就要自己執<br />\n叫香港人唔好亂拋垃圾都難啦，成地煙頭 廢紙等<br />\n更何況執盤"},{"pid":"46adbc8c47d6e70c06d426f861cf77e02c6f4969","tid":399911,"uid":22808,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:24:31.000Z","msg":"靚女可能會執佢一劑"},{"pid":"26d0899494549eb2463abcc8bb1691b83dca4dce","tid":399911,"uid":30857,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:35:52.000Z","msg":"香港麥當勞不嬲唔使自己執 攞其它地方講做乜 你唔好食大家樂自己執埋"},{"pid":"b14760ccffe049314878012b9e4a1a381edc075a","tid":399911,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:44:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"803eba85d3100b823994576692f003efff72a31b","tid":399911,"uid":58393,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:45:10.000Z","msg":"食得乾淨啲 唔好成枱碎、垃圾 又或者個盤都係茄汁<br />\n執拾餐盤係員工既職責<br />\n但令到人做得輕鬆啲 就係一般食客都做到既舉手之勞<br />\n慳左既時間可以用黎清潔其他地方/比佢輕鬆啲<br />\n而且其他食客都會覺得你好自重 有公德心"},{"pid":"bb5110ad459394e5f2d16f290c9c44f474c4c95c","tid":399911,"uid":77201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:47:44.000Z","msg":"係佢未變中資之前會放係個垃圾桶上面等職員搞又唔洗騰黎騰去<br />\n中資之後再冇食過"},{"pid":"ada8d271cbf572f177666b301ea0eb41e02bdd42","tid":399911,"uid":142819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:48:54.000Z","msg":"例牌答案 靚女望住咪執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17e95b2043e1ba25eca04ebb9d393a59f06948c","tid":399911,"uid":26003,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"有教養既人自然會執，<br />\n同偽善冇關<br />\n<br />\n利申: 外國畢業"},{"pid":"54204b86d066d6b530eebe293e64e707399f08a8","tid":399911,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:52:05.000Z","msg":"上面嗰班連字都未撚識嘅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我汁你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"2b5ed9491bd1bc3fa541201e2d9ffc939cdb42e6","tid":399911,"uid":12252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:52:29.000Z","msg":"有靚女附近會執"},{"pid":"ffd30dad8c7c0eed0b936241de912d46b0029df4","tid":399911,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:53:52.000Z","msg":"喺日本會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4b24b54f3718850c027b68267cd1111a76c052","tid":399911,"uid":140754,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:54:46.000Z","msg":"自從去左台灣同日本<br />\n就學識左要執"},{"pid":"5ee849864a69890fdfd4ee6fc6f7635a94d0df50","tid":399911,"uid":96472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"人流多時，你執反而幫倒忙<br />\n不過有時幫到咪幫囉，睇你人品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a809e722469a2160e9e05466f39702e0c41112cb","tid":399911,"uid":23451,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:55:55.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n外國係冇請人執盤<br />\n但香港係有請人專執盤<br />\n<br />\n所以根本唔關有冇公德心既事<br />\n係外國會執，係香港唔會執<br />\n<br />\n利申 做過m記兩星期"},{"pid":"95e2a244dba052938459e2190dcd4bc70b3e3007","tid":399911,"uid":79427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:56:58.000Z","msg":"執啦，唔執下個人點食"},{"pid":"ffc3a30baeddb4449eca28f40926422b0401dbc1","tid":399911,"uid":10844,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"唔好話老麥，飲茶都會啦<br />\n執好哂d碗碟再換埋枱布<br />\n咁先顯得自己有教養"},{"pid":"fc92418ce0f961302cba64f90e25354d03fee937","tid":399911,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"我每次一定都會執，順便掃埋地同拖地，幫手換埋廁所廁紙先會走"},{"pid":"3b3117f79bd19bdb731433888a94f174f0d97f3b","tid":399911,"uid":90457,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"自己一個食就多數都執<br />\n有次同人食，我執自己嗰份就俾人指手劃腳<br />\n人哋份糧包埋，幫佢咪益咗佢<br />\n第一句我聽到，我都覺得自己多事<br />\n第二句我聽到，我就覺得他很支那"},{"pid":"0d180ef471a49abd592507380c93f3c5dbcfe91d","tid":399911,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:02:26.000Z","msg":"唔會執 仲特登倒晒落地下 吹"},{"pid":"f56a074f3bf299db66c544dc2a228fcefe590d84","tid":399911,"uid":13616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩係日本返黎, 食左幾餐老麥<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地全撚部人都會自己執盤</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n仲要自己做垃圾分類</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁人地國家文化係咁<br />\n但係香港文化不嬲都係有清潔會執<br />\n咁做咩要執 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39ab9420027fb9b