n但隔離枱有班中學生都冇買野食係到溫書同有幾個西裝佬係到等客定涼冷氣反而冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120364efc38fa8ea078d2d25e01f8d0d80d62731","tid":399911,"uid":37566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩係日本返黎, 食左幾餐老麥<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地全撚部人都會自己執盤</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n大字做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多地方都係<br />\n得支國同香港係有人幫你執"},{"pid":"01bd5f75fb967d7107386c6ab93c1a34b1501b65","tid":399911,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T07:13:52.000Z","msg":"而家好多m記都貼咗個牌叫你自己執，點知上次我自己執，又俾個阿姐話經理睇住佢做嘢，我執咗佢無嘢做會俾人罵"},{"pid":"c7f9f10b9ffbf928cc07de45c14e5be0719d8fb6","tid":399911,"uid":147432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"會幫佢擺係垃圾桶上面個個area"},{"pid":"3a3e3e054c7c67a0d8b318a6ec85ac8be46ce561","tid":399911,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T07:38:23.000Z","msg":"香港既文化執黎多餘,又唔係做垃圾分類<br />\n倒完你又唔似阿姐咁有塊布叫抹下佢<br />\n一個唔好彩有人漏左d醬係度都咪話唔煩到阿姐<br />\n唔係話人地好就要跟"},{"pid":"32be49d00021cbed641c8b92e49be72da5fb296f","tid":399911,"uid":90174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T07:40:16.000Z","msg":"正常外國人係會食埋個盤"},{"pid":"0332a2c5d621324db99615e0076a2223255d13ad","tid":399911,"uid":384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T07:41:31.000Z","msg":"入左u之後食街外m記都會自己執 慣左手勢"}]}